    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is an affordable way to get into a car without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who wants basic transportation, a project, or a practical low-cost option. Priced to sell and presented honestly, it offers strong value for someone who sees the opportunity.",
