    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project, parts car, or a budget-friendly runabout with some life left in it? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for the right buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. Great candidate for someone handy, a first project, or anyone wanting a cheap set of wheels without spending a fortune. Priced to sell and worth a look if you appreciate value and potential.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with strong mechanical upside. The engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to be a great foundation for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at. Cosmetic wear and age-related needs are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. A good candidate for a dependable daily with some attention, or a smart platform for a clean-up build.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap driver. Rough, but it runs and gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true underdog with plenty of personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn charm that makes every drive feel like a story in progress. It\u2019s an affordable way to get behind the wheel of something with presence, character, and real potential\u2014whether you want a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a platform to make your own. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect, and that\u2019s exactly the appeal: simple, straightforward, and ready for its next chapter with someone who sees the value in a car that still has more to give.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable path to dependable basic transportation or a solid starting point for a project-minded buyer. It shows its age and wear, but it remains a practical value for someone seeking low-cost ownership with room to make it their own. A straightforward opportunity at an attractive price.",
      "price": 4950.0,
