      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a handy backup, or a fun little project. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is, and with a bit of TLC, there\u2019s a lot to like here. If you want something cheap, straightforward, and worth a look, come check it out.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Well-priced project or budget daily with solid mechanical upside. This car starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with an engine that pulls cleanly through the rev range and a drivetrain that feels usable as-is. Not a showroom piece, but a straightforward platform for someone who appreciates honest metal and a chassis with plenty of life left in it. A good candidate for light restoration, commuter duty, or weekend tinkering, with the kind of character and usability that\u2019s getting harder to find at this price point. Priced to sell for someone who wants affordable entry and room to improve.",
